  "hasWeakener": [],
  "hasDecisionRecord": {
    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-accepted-20260419",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per the MRL 2 scoping decision, consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all five operating points with maximum normalised error of 9.3%, within the defined validation uncertainty threshold. The assessment team acknowledges that the primary experimental dataset (MOR-2025-047) carries a dataVintage of 2025-10-09, approximately 25 days prior to the model revision date of 2025-11-03. The revision adjusted SST k-ω model constants (C_mu from 0.09 to 0.085) and near-wall y+ treatment; engineering judgement confirms this change does not alter the experimental boundary conditions or measurement traceability captured in MOR-2025-047. The team concludes the dataset remains valid for the revised model without formal re-validation. The package is accepted at Medium assurance level for the CPB COU.",
